reviews.review_text: PHILLLL Phil is well demonstrated in this fine show! Thanks for the upload!
I was born on the 39th......... We'll just leave it at that.

My First DEAD Show! And the Journey Continues Piecing together the years with ticket stubs & a Covid-19 timeline... Life is Good. And, I am Grateful have this archive to unroll the years. "Strong Island" Energy!
